{"tid":1908673,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"求各位英文大師解讀，請問呢封信係咪代表我可以完全refund IELTS學費","createTime":"2020-03-03T12:19:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-05T15:16:43.000Z","uid":212080,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c3ce973c5ff1c4ebea0db64aab700c5a6e4f4ff1","tid":1908673,"uid":212080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T12:19:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M2QeMOZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM2QeMOZ.png&h=9191e0d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n是咁的，本身之前報咗2月8號IELTS，用作non jupas用，嗰陣都溫咗半個幾月，但佢因為個肺炎取消咗。<br />\n跟住可以免費refund或者報之後嘅考試，咁我就報咗22號嘅。<br />\n到咗17號佢又話要延後，咁我未有offer唯有繼續報啦，就報咗3月4號（聽日）。<br />\n點知18號收到offer，佢本身同我講3月嘅IELTS可以正常舉行，冇得refund。<br />\n但佢啱啱突然send咗呢封email畀我，係咪即係代表我唔使考？<br />\n請睇睇highlight嗰部分：<br />\nhave had a test postponed due to the test being scheduled during the period of the British Council in Hong Kong&rsquo;s services suspension<br />\n麻煩各位英文大師解讀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84730f64e8ac4f82c1e5b565c1174a0a74cee09f","tid":1908673,"uid":308251,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T12:27:29.000Z","msg":"佢話可以延期或者退錢，如果你個考期係喺British council停止服務期間<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講真，如果你咁都睇唔明，咁你都無謂考。<br />\n唔係笑你，係真誠嘅建議。"},{"pid":"05f4ff924f0c25c84f866bee36586736aad93aa9","tid":1908673,"uid":329320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T12:28:32.000Z","msg":"按照你嘅情況可以選擇全費退款或者延期三個月內考"},{"pid":"7baa843e1854b6b2581a0f30e29d5015585fa36f","tid":1908673,"uid":301171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T12:29:16.000Z","msg":"3月5號先開始可以考 你3月4號未必有 除非你係跟學校/用電腦考 <br />\n你可以揀延遲或者全數退款<br />\n仲係唔肯定既就快快手send個email俾佢地啦"},{"pid":"437c8783fd1e56bbf9bc739c44094f925d255310","tid":1908673,"uid":201182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3ce973c5ff1c4ebea0db64aab700c5a6e4f4ff1","tid":1908673,"uid":212080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T12:19:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M2QeMOZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM2QeMOZ.png&h=9191e0d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n是咁的，本身之前報咗2月8號IELTS，用作non jupas用，嗰陣都溫咗半個幾月，但佢因為個肺炎取消咗。<br />\n跟住可以免費refund或者報之後嘅考試，咁我就報咗22號嘅。<br />\n到咗17號佢又話要延後，咁我未有offer唯有繼續報啦，就報咗3月4號（聽日）。<br />\n點知18號收到offer，佢本身同我講3月嘅IELTS可以正常舉行，冇得refund。<br />\n但佢啱啱突然send咗呢封email畀我，係咪即係代表我唔使考？<br />\n請睇睇highlight嗰部分：<br />\nhave had a test postponed due to the test being scheduled during the period of the British Council in Hong Kong&rsquo;s services suspension<br />\n麻煩各位英文大師解讀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T15:16:43.000Z","msg":"唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係呢個post都留左次言<br />\n 想請問下樓主之前揀defer個時,係咪D日子任揀? 定係有條件?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n心急人上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}